			SHAREWARE
	ReqDoor		File Request door for Dialog users.
			CARDWARE, works in STDIO.
	CheckAlias	Alias Checker/editor for DLG.
			CARDWARE.

	 New version of ReqDoor and MagicFile  can be requested
	from my bbs. Magic Names are:

