@node final "Final Words"

 @{b}@{u}Final Words@{ub}@{uu}

Kirk: 	"Whales have been on Earth far earlier than man."
Spock: 	"Ten  million years earlier.  And humpbacks were heavily
	hunted   by   man.    They've  been  extinct  since  the
	twenty-first  century.   It  is  possible  that an alien
	intelligence  sent  the probe to determine why they lost
	contact."
McCoy:	"My god."
--"STIV:TVH", Stardate 8390

Nagilum: "To  understand death, I must amass information on every
	 aspect  of it.  The experiments shouldn't take more than
	 a third of your crew, maybe half."
--"Where Silence Has Lease", Stardate 42

